channel.title: M-Sides - Maland2016 [Album]
channel.description:
SoundCloud edition! Yep, I _finally_ put M-Sides on SoundCloud. Take a listen and please leave me criticism, positive or negative. Which songs did you like, which didn't you like, which ones can I improve and remaster someday?
[Listen here!](https://soundcloud.com/maland2016/sets/m-sides-full-album)
